title: Iwin Games - Something Special - New HOG - Wendy99
description:
Something Special - 162.24 MB



Something Special let's you see America - and hidden objects - like never before: through the 
eyes of Zoe, a young woman seeking that Something Special. As her wacky Aunt Zandra gives her a 
push in the right direction - clear across the USA - join Zoe for a road trip to fascinating REAL 
landmarks located in our own backyards! The Lunchbox Museum, Cockroach Hall of Fame, Elvis 
Extravaganza and many more. Something Special is a light-hearted, bizarre, charming new take on 
America!
